1
00:00:01,980 --> 00:00:04,107
为什么你快死了 妈妈？
Why are you dying, Mama?

2
00:00:04,182 --> 00:00:06,275
我的时候到了
It's my time.

3
00:00:06,351 --> 00:00:09,411
因为我的时候到了
It's just my time.

4
00:00:09,488 --> 00:00:11,513
现在…
Oh, now...

5
00:00:12,591 --> 00:00:15,151
你不用害怕 宝贝
don't you be afraid, sweet heart .

6
00:00:15,228 --> 00:00:18,629
死亡只是生命的一部分
Death is just a part of life .

7
00:00:18,698 --> 00:00:22,657
是我们注定要面对的
Something we're all destined to do.

8
00:00:22,737 --> 00:00:25,069
我并不知道
I didn't know it,

9
00:00:25,139 --> 00:00:28,074
但我注定要做你的妈妈
but I was destined to be your mama.

10
00:00:28,143 --> 00:00:30,873
我就尽力做好
I did the best I could.

11
00:00:30,946 --> 00:00:32,880
你做得很好
You did good.

12
00:00:32,949 --> 00:00:39,219
嗯…我相信你能实现自己的命运
Well...I happen to believe you make your own destiny .

13
00:00:39,289 --> 00:00:43,817
你要凭着上帝所给予的做到最好
You have to do the best with what God gave you.

14
00:00:47,332 --> 00:00:49,926
我的命运是什么 妈妈？
What's my destiny, Mama?

15
00:00:50,002 --> 00:00:54,439
你要自己去弄明白
You're going to have to figure that out for yourself.

16
00:00:55,776 --> 00:00:58,711
人生就像一盒各式各样的巧克力
Life is a box of chocolates, Forrest.

17
00:00:58,779 --> 00:01:01,714
你永远不知道下一块将会是哪种
You never know what you're going to get.

18
00:01:01,783 --> 00:01:04,718
妈妈总有办法把事情说清楚
Mama always hada way of explaining things

19
00:01:04,786 --> 00:01:06,720
让我也能听明白
so I could understand them.

20
00:01:06,788 --> 00:01:08,255
我会想念你的 福雷斯
I will miss you, Forrest.

21
00:01:09,992 --> 00:01:12,256
她得了癌症
She had got the cancer

22
00:01:12,327 --> 00:01:14,261
在星期二去世了
and died on a Tuesday.

23
00:01:14,330 --> 00:01:16,924
我给她买了顶新帽子
I bought her a new hat

24
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:19,025
上面有很多小花
with little flowers on it.

25
00:01:21,972 --> 00:01:24,668
我要说的说是这么多了
And that's all I have to say about that.

